{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_51_01",
  "title": "kana",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――雑誌の打ち合わせ中",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』ですか！？\nわ～！　kana、この企画大好きなんです！",
      "startTime": 4.8000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルが誕生日にやりたいことを叶えてくれる、雑誌\nの名物企画ですよね。いつか出たいなって思ってました",
      "startTime": 11.8000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.8666655303
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "（……って表向きには言っといてやるけどさぁ）\n（誕生日ギリギリでオファーとか、なんなの？）",
      "startTime": 21.1666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.6333335957
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "（急にやりたいことなんて思いつかないし。それに）\n（「他にも誰か呼んで、誌面を華やかにしたい」？）",
      "startTime": 28.4000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "（はあ……呼べって言うなら、テキトーに呼ぶけど）\n（引き立て役にぴったりで、暇そうなアイドルか……あ）",
      "startTime": 38.0666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.099998355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "決めました！　kana、お誕生日は大好きなスリクス\nのメンバーと過ごしたいです！　具体的には――",
      "startTime": 49.7333334049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 55.2333326818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、どういうこと！？　なんで私達が\nあんたの誕生日企画に出なきゃいけないのよ！",
      "startTime": 59.0639980024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "同意見ね。仕事を口実に嫌がらせをしているなら\nやめてもらえるかしら",
      "startTime": 66.9430876256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざそんなことをしなくても\nお互い、日頃から十分気分が悪いと思うけれど",
      "startTime": 71.1584403993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "うるさいなー\nせっかく仕事持って来てあげたのに、何が不満な訳？",
      "startTime": 76.400005452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "全部よ、全部。何が『大好きなスリクスのメンバーと\n過ごしたい』、よ。うわあ……言ってて鳥肌立ってきた",
      "startTime": 85.5666660151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "どうせ『kanaの引き立て役には、あいつらが\nちょうどいいっしょ』とか思って言ったんでしょうね",
      "startTime": 93.1224897465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "分かってんならいいじゃん。山田さんと武田さんは\nいつも通り、脇役になってくれてればいいから",
      "startTime": 100.3333403112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "あんた、それが人にものを頼む態度？\n私は嫌。絶対やらない。あと、山田って呼ぶな！",
      "startTime": 107.9000008744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "えー、山田さんってば酷ーい\n個人の感情でグループの仕事を断らないでくださーい",
      "startTime": 115.1543853322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "だから山田って呼ぶなってば！",
      "startTime": 119.8666759572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、確かにkanaの言うことにも一理あるわね\n一応、グループの仕事ではあるわ",
      "startTime": 127.0031833491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "内容はともかく、メディアへの露出が減っている\nスリクスにとって、チャンスでもあるし",
      "startTime": 132.5641743264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "……いいわ、参加してあげる。汚れ仕事の一つや二つ\nこなしてこそ、真のアイドルだもの",
      "startTime": 140.2000018916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "誰の誕生日が汚れ仕事だ！",
      "startTime": 142.8666744313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ、仕方ないわね。で、何すればいいんだっけ？\nkanaの顔にケーキでもぶつければいいの？",
      "startTime": 152.433332642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "どこのバラエティ番組だよ。とりあえず今決まってる\nのは、お店で食事しながらトークするって感じかなー",
      "startTime": 159.8666746618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "これまでを振り返りつつ、主役のkanaを二人が褒め\nちぎる、ⅢXの本音トークのコーナーって感じで",
      "startTime": 168.8754789831,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "何が本音よ。矛盾してる上に、最悪のコーナーね……\nっていうか、それしか決まってないってこと？",
      "startTime": 178.4101562581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "kanaのトーク力なら、それだけで記事になるっしょ\n編集部の人も、納得してたみたいだし",
      "startTime": 185.4089588974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "一体、どう丸めこんだのかしら。普通こういう場合\nトーク以外にも、ゲームとかで盛り上がるものだけど",
      "startTime": 193.340105065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "へ～、武田さん、物知りじゃん\nさすが、芸歴が長い人は違うな～",
      "startTime": 199.9942789139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……そもそも具体的にどんなことをやるか\nちゃんと決めておきなさいよ。あんたの企画でしょ",
      "startTime": 207.4000003658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "決めてるっての。映えるスポットで、映えるケーキを\n食べて、最後にSNS用の写真を撮って終わり",
      "startTime": 214.4999876502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "ってか、余白があるなら、二人がなんか用意してきてよ\nkanaは主役だし。お祝いしてもらう側でしょー？",
      "startTime": 222.8242704871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "相変わらず、自分のSNSのことしか考えていないわね\n……誕生日なら、プレゼントも必要じゃないかしら",
      "startTime": 232.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、そういうの！　きゃはっ、二人がプレゼント\nくれるなんて嬉しい～。どんないいものくれるんだろ～",
      "startTime": 241.3829709443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "なんであげるって決まってるのよ。っていうかあげるに\nしても、面倒だから先に何がほしいか教えなさいよね",
      "startTime": 250.3666670325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　それは、やらせみたいでつまんなくない？\n大好きなkanaのために、二人が選んでほしいな～",
      "startTime": 259.7641135997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "あんたって本当に面倒くさいわね……",
      "startTime": 264.5666164481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "仕事とはいえ、余計なことを言ったかしら",
      "startTime": 268.099968092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
